column16: Ronald Torreyes singles on a ground ball to left fielder Andrew Benintendi, deflected by third baseman Brock Holt.   Clint Frazier to 3rd.
Austin Romine flies out to right fielder Mookie Betts.
Clint Frazier singles on a ground ball to left fielder Andrew Benintendi.
Didi Gregorius pops out to third baseman Deven Marrero in foul territory.
Matt Holliday pops out to shortstop Xander Bogaerts.
Aaron Judge singles on a soft ground ball to pitcher Austin Maddox.
Chase Headley flies out to right fielder Mookie Betts.
Ramon Torres grounds out, second baseman Josh Rutledge to first baseman Mitch Moreland.
Alcides Escobar singles on a line drive to left fielder Andrew Benintendi.
Cheslor Cuthbert flies out to right fielder Mookie Betts.
Carlos Correa pops out to shortstop Xander Bogaerts.
Jose Altuve grounds out softly, third baseman Josh Rutledge to first baseman Mitch Moreland.
Marwin Gonzalez flies out to right fielder Mookie Betts.
